query:
SELECT d.*, a.assetId, ast.name as assetName 
FROM deficiencies d 
LEFT JOIN assessments a ON d.assessmentId = a.id 
LEFT JOIN assets ast ON a.assetId = ast.id
WHERE ast.name LIKE '%Comox%' OR ast.address LIKE '%Comox%'
LIMIT 20;
